26:28.788 --> 26:31.657
So they leaked it.

26:31.657 --> 26:32.925
And I do not like it.

26:32.925 --> 26:35.127
We need the reins
back in our hands.

26:35.127 --> 26:36.162
Understood.

26:36.162 --> 26:38.230
You want me to stay
on this Axe/Decker thing?

26:38.230 --> 26:40.866
[Chuck]
No. Set that aside.

26:40.866 --> 26:42.301
Until we know
at least as much

26:42.301 --> 26:44.070
as this fucking reporter
knows,

26:44.070 --> 26:45.938
let's keep the brights
on Steven Birch.

26:45.938 --> 26:47.039
All right.

26:47.039 --> 26:48.174
[Chuck]
Get me every article

26:48.174 --> 26:51.911
Randy Kornbluth wrote
in the past year.

26:51.911 --> 26:53.713
All of Mike Dimonda's
articles, too.

26:53.713 --> 26:55.247
We'll start there.

27:08.694 --> 27:10.096
Mike.

27:10.096 --> 27:12.398
[car door opens]

27:15.835 --> 27:18.337
Good parlor trick,
knowing my address.

27:18.337 --> 27:20.706
That'll look like
a fun intimidation tactic

27:20.706 --> 27:21.707
when I write this up.

27:21.707 --> 27:24.176
Oh. You're not
writing this up.

27:24.176 --> 27:25.845
Because that would be
a small win,

27:25.845 --> 27:28.247
and you're not in it
for small wins.

27:28.247 --> 27:30.416
No, you've come too far.
Too young an age for that.

27:30.416 --> 27:32.385
I'm in it because people
deserve to know the truth

27:32.385 --> 27:34.053
about power and money and --
Whoa. Wait a minute.

27:34.053 --> 27:36.722
What are you, Glenn Greenwald
all of a sudden?

27:36.722 --> 27:37.323
Come on.

27:37.323 --> 27:38.391
[both chuckle]

27:40.226 --> 27:42.962
You know, I've, uh,
I've been reading...

27:42.962 --> 27:45.264
Randy Kornbluth lately.

27:45.264 --> 27:48.000
He usually covers
state politics.

27:48.000 --> 27:50.936
He hasn't had a hard
business story in 18 months,

27:50.936 --> 27:52.304
but all of a sudden,

27:52.304 --> 27:54.907
he hooks into
a full-blown crime story --

27:54.907 --> 27:56.375
on Steven Birch.

27:57.777 --> 27:59.311
His article quotes

27:59.311 --> 28:02.148
former federal prosecutor
James Robbins,

28:02.148 --> 28:03.816
who says
that the connection

28:03.816 --> 28:06.352
between hedge funds
and company officials

28:06.352 --> 28:08.187
must be probed.

28:09.789 --> 28:12.291
You know who else
likes quoting James Robbins?

28:12.291 --> 28:13.926
You.

28:13.926 --> 28:16.262
Seven times
in the past six months.

28:16.262 --> 28:18.097
He's a widely respected source
with connections --

28:18.097 --> 28:20.199
He's a fucking
rent-a-quote.

28:20.199 --> 28:23.369
I know you really wrote
the Birch story,

28:23.369 --> 28:27.907
and I think I know why
you chose to hide that fact.

28:27.907 --> 28:29.809
If I am
such a careerist,

28:29.809 --> 28:31.310
why would I ever hide
something that good?

28:31.310 --> 28:33.879
'Cause you thought
it would endear you to someone.

28:36.082 --> 28:37.283
What you should have done,

28:37.283 --> 28:40.019
if you were really playing
an elevated game,

28:40.019 --> 28:42.455
was come to me
with what you had.

28:42.455 --> 28:44.190
See, if I had
something better to give you

28:44.190 --> 28:45.491
in exchange
for you holding on to it --

28:45.491 --> 28:46.959
You have never been willing

28:46.959 --> 28:48.394
to play any kind of game
with me.

28:48.394 --> 28:50.963
I didn't know you were ready
to play in the bigs, man.

28:50.963 --> 28:52.498
Now I do.

28:52.498 --> 28:54.166
So, these are the rules.

28:54.166 --> 28:55.734
You tell me
who fed you that --

28:55.734 --> 28:57.336
No.

28:57.336 --> 28:59.872
I'm gonna head inside.

28:59.872 --> 29:01.807
Because this conversation
has peaked,

29:01.807 --> 29:05.177
and you  don't
get to tell me the rules.

29:05.177 --> 29:06.745
You're correct.

29:06.745 --> 29:08.914
I'm not gonna write up
this ambush.

29:08.914 --> 29:10.349
But I can.

29:10.349 --> 29:13.285
[Michael]
Anytime I want to.

29:13.285 --> 29:15.321
So think about that
the next time

29:15.321 --> 29:17.790
you try and bar me
from a press conference

29:17.790 --> 29:19.358
or dodge my call.

29:19.358 --> 29:21.127
Have a good night.

29:23.062 --> 29:24.463
[keys jingle]

29:24.463 --> 29:27.466
[door opens, closes]

