52:02.520 --> 52:04.288
Which is why
I am presenting you

52:04.288 --> 52:08.726
with a check for $25 million

52:08.726 --> 52:10.828
minus 16,

52:10.828 --> 52:13.364
which leaves you
with $9 million.

52:13.364 --> 52:15.333
[gasps]
That is bullshit!

52:15.333 --> 52:16.634
[man] This is unacceptable.
[Chad] Ellis, this is bullshit.

52:16.634 --> 52:19.203
We will walk out of here if
you don't honor the full amount.

52:19.203 --> 52:20.872
No, you won't.

52:20.872 --> 52:23.207
You need this $9 million.

52:23.207 --> 52:25.776
Because none of you --
not one --

52:25.776 --> 52:27.712
has done
a single day of work

52:27.712 --> 52:29.914
from the moment your miserable
prick of a grandfather

52:29.914 --> 52:32.483
fell facedown in the sand
in Palm Beach.

52:32.483 --> 52:35.186
And after reviewing
your holdings,

52:35.186 --> 52:37.221
your business interests,
your debts,

52:37.221 --> 52:39.223
I know that this check
is the only thing

52:39.223 --> 52:42.393
standing between your family
and bankruptcy.

52:42.393 --> 52:45.663
So pick it up,
put it in your pocket,

52:45.663 --> 52:47.632
and walk out of here.

52:47.632 --> 52:49.901
Or I  will.

