Let's get out of here.

53:02.547 --> 53:03.948
Mnh!

53:10.488 --> 53:12.590
[Sean]
So, now the Axelrod name

53:12.590 --> 53:17.261
will be forever affixed
to this building for all time.

53:17.261 --> 53:18.629
Or until some guy
richer than me

53:18.629 --> 53:20.331
wants it to come down.

53:22.233 --> 53:23.968
You really
started something.

